137→// HasBuiltinWebSearch reports whether the Claude request declared a search tool
138→// that should be routed to Codex built-in web_search on the Claude -> GPT
139→// compatibility path. This includes Anthropic's built-in web_search tool and
140→// Claude Code's generic WebSearch function tool.
141→func HasBuiltinWebSearch(rawJSON []byte) bool {
